---
// Contact section
---

<section id="contact" class="section contact-section">
	<div class="section-content">
		<h2>Kontaktuj nás</h2>
		<p>Máte otázky? Chcete sa informovať o našich kurzoch? Napíšte nám alebo nás kontaktujte pomocou formulára nižšie.</p>
		<div class="contact-box">
			<div class="contact-info">
				<h3>Informácie</h3>
				<p><strong>Email:</strong> hello@verbal.school</p>
				<p><strong>Telefón:</strong> +421 2 1234 5678</p>
				<p><strong>Adresa:</strong> Bratislava, Slovakia</p>
			</div>
			<form class="contact-form">
				<input type="text" placeholder="Vaše meno" required>
				<input type="email" placeholder="Váš email" required>
				<textarea placeholder="Vaša správa" rows="5" required></textarea>
				<button type="submit" class="btn primary">Poslať správu</button>
			</form>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.section {
		padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		min-height: 60vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.section-content {
		width: 100%;
	}

	.section h2 {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
		margin: 0 0 2rem;
		color: #e6eef8;
	}

	.section p {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: rgba(230, 238, 248, 0.85);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.contact-section {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f1724 0%, #071124 100%);
	}

	.contact-box {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.contact-info {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02));
		border-radius: 14px;
		padding: 2rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
	}

	.contact-info h3 {
		color: #06b6d4;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.contact-info p {
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.contact-form {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.contact-form input,
	.contact-form textarea {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
		border-radius: 10px;
		padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
		color: #e6eef8;
		font-family: inherit;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.contact-form input::placeholder,
	.contact-form textarea::placeholder {
		color: rgba(230, 238, 248, 0.5);
	}

	.contact-form input:focus,
	.contact-form textarea:focus {
		outline: none;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
		border-color: rgba(106, 17, 203, 0.5);
	}

	.btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.65rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 10px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 600;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, #7c3aed, #06b6d4);
		color: #021018;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.18);
		transform: translateY(0);
		transition: transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease;
		border: none;
		cursor: pointer;
		align-self: flex-start;
	}

	.btn:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.22);
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.contact-box {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
